# Coverage Exclusion Patterns (Single Source of Truth)
# =====================================================
# This file is read by: cmake/coverage.cmake, .githooks/pre-commit, .github/workflows/codecov.yml
# Adding new exclusions: Add pattern here, all three will pick it up automatically.
# Format: One glob pattern per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# POLICY: Only exclude code that genuinely cannot be unit tested.
# Adding new exclusions requires PR review with justification.

# System headers and third-party
/usr/*
*/external/*
*/tests/*

# WebSocket network I/O (requires live server connections)
*/exchange/binance_ws.hpp
*/exchange/binance_futures_ws.hpp

# UDP receiver (epoll + recvmmsg syscalls)
*/network/udp_receiver.hpp

# IPC shared memory syscall failure paths (shm_open/mmap/ftruncate)
*/ipc/shared_config.hpp
*/ipc/shared_portfolio_state.hpp
*/ipc/shared_event_log.hpp
*/ipc/shared_ledger.hpp
*/ipc/shared_metrics_snapshot.hpp
*/ipc/shared_tuner_state.hpp
*/ipc/udp_telemetry.hpp
